desc:
Please create a sproc for me to select the activity for a Branch in SearchWorks. Basically, give me the last 50 events happening within the branch as well as the documents that arrived combined into one dataset. Please also include login statistic (if possible). For example, "Yasser Ogier signed in."

Fields needed:

Description (Search or Document or "Authenticated")
User involved (Name)
Date of Event
Search Type / Document Type / 0 (for login)
IsDocument (bool)
CallerModule
MenuObject

See screenshot below for example.
name: SW - Activity Log
